       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. RECORD-WRITER.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT REPORT-FILE ASSIGN TO "report.dat".
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  REPORT-FILE.
       01  REPORT-RECORD.
           05  REPORT-ID PIC X(4).
           05  REPORT-NAME PIC X(24).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  REPORT-COUNT PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.
       01  WORK-REPORT.
           05  WORK-ID PIC X(4).
           05  WORK-NAME PIC X(24).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
           OPEN OUTPUT REPORT-FILE.
           MOVE "0001" TO WORK-ID.
           MOVE "INITIAL ENTRY" TO WORK-NAME.
           MOVE WORK-REPORT TO REPORT-RECORD.
           WRITE REPORT-RECORD.
           ADD 1 TO REPORT-COUNT.
           CLOSE REPORT-FILE.
           STOP RUN.
